## 2026-02-22 — Dependency update notes

### typescript-eslint v8.56+
- Having both `project` and `projectService` in `parserOptions` is now an error
- `@st1ggy/linter-config` sets both; strip `project` via `Object.fromEntries` filter in `eslint.config.js`

### @st1ggy/linter-config v2.42+
- Now ships type declarations — remove `@ts-expect-error` from config file imports
- `import/default` rule may produce false positives for subpath exports; suppress with `// eslint-disable-next-line import/default`

